data.description: The Boca ll model was completed this year and is ready for that family looking for new construction without the wait.  This well appointed home has 4 bedrooms and 4 baths. It has a separate dining room as well as a gourmet kitchen with double ovens. White 42'' cabinets and glass tile backsplash complemented by a large island with eat-in counter. This home has 2 additional flex areas, definitely suited to the couple that works from home.  Open concept family room with a fireplace that has color changing insert. Tile throughout busy areas gives the look of marble. Principal bedroom with extremely large bathroom and walk- in closets. Laundry room and separate mud room. Upstairs bonus room/ bedroom with bath and walk-in closet.  Beautiful home with lanai and on a water lot. Must See!
